Notes: UWO ranked 19th in the NCAA Div. III by D3hoops.com...UWO defeated UWSP
72-44 on Jan. 24 in Stevens Point...UWSP took the lead for good at 25-22 and
built three 10-point leads (40-30, 42-32 and 45-35) before UWO cut deficit to
49-47 with 2:43 left...UWSP's Cerrato had 14 points...Game featured 16 blocks.
